319
00:20:36,235 --> 00:20:37,532
<i>... and sang company songs. </i>

320
00:20:46,111 --> 00:20:47,942
<i>I mean, we were
these scruffy crazies... </i>

321
00:20:48,113 --> 00:20:52,277
<i>... messing around with computer stuff
